f, der Genetiker Markus Hengstschäger, die iranische Künstlerin Shirin Neshat, der Neurobiologe Joachim Bauer, der Soziologe Hartmut Rosa oder die Regisseurin Jacqueline Kornmüller.   aWe are all too familiar with the complex new triggers of geopolitical uncertainty: a financial system that knows no boundaries, renationalization, desecularization, and both the bright and dark sides of technological revolutions. Yet the big picture often eludes us. GlobArt-Academy 2014 is devoted to addressing these issues.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 4aArbeit. 4aBildung. 4aEhtik. 4aFilm. 4aKunst. 4aMensch-Maschine. 4aPhilosophie. 4aSoziologie. 4aTechnik. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh1 aGlobArt, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2015z9783110438741oZDB-23-DSW0 cprintz978311041574240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311041580340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110415803423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110415803.jpg  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSWb2015